      <div>
        <p><strong>Background:</strong> Grey 20 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#ededf0</code></p>

        <p><strong>Text:</strong> Grey 90 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#0c0c0d</code></p>

        <h5 id="buttons">BUTTONS</h5>

        <p>Default: Blue 60 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#0a84ff</code></p>

        <p>Hover: Blue 70 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#0060df</code></p>

        <p>Pressed: Blue 80 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">#003eaa</code></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h3 id="icon">Icon</h3>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <p><img src="../images/message-bars/i-gen.svg" alt="pairing example" /></p>

      <div>
        <p>Icons may provide additional clarity. Icons should be placed to the left of a title or message. These glyphs (16x16) can be found in the <a href="http://design.firefox.com/icons/">icons library</a>.</p>

        <p>Icons always have a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">4px</code> padding all around.</p>

        <p><strong>Type:</strong> <a href="http://design.firefox.com/icons/viewer/#identity%20icon%20hover">Identity Icon Hover</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

