<h2 id="behavior">Behavior</h2>

<h3 id="dismissible">Dismissible</h3>

<div class="grid-2">
  <p><img src="../images/message-bars/ghost-btn.svg" alt="Dismissable behavior" /></p>

  <p>Unless they contain critical information, message bars should be dismissible by clicking or tapping the ghost button, placed in the top right corner.</p>
</div>

<h3 id="call-to-action">Call to Action</h3>

<div class="grid-2">
  <p><img src="../images/message-bars/mb-action-example.svg" alt="message bar in action" /></p>

  <div>
    <p>Add one or two <a href="buttons.html#micro">micro-buttons</a> to the message bar if users need to take an action after reading the message.</p>

